cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a new exploration strategy for sample-efficient episodic control methods in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses Atari games as a benchmark, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-categories.
